    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I am so excited to find a new home for this absolute gem. It\u2019s in truly pristine condition\u2014seriously, it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. Not a single scratch or hiccup to be found. You\u2019ve gotta come see it for yourself\u2014you\u2019re going to fall in love! \u2728",
