    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the S54 high-revving straight-six, complete with individual throttle bodies and a documented VANOS overhaul using Beisan components. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission offers precise shift gates, delivering power to the rear wheels via a factory variable M differential lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the cooling system has been refreshed with a high-flow water pump and aluminum radiator. The suspension geometry remains stock, maintaining the legendary 50/50 weight distribution. This is an analog masterpiece with zero deferred maintenance, ready for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
