      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This car is in showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather upholstery still retains its original factory scent and shows no signs of bolstering wear or creasing. Every electronic component and interface operates with precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service history documented exclusively at certified dealerships. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
